{
  "stem": "2067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Shortly, maybe a couple of weeks after, we had found shelter there, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Dottie ?] had to leave her house, too, when a search by the SS from house to house in the street where we lived almost caught her and her younger brother.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They escaped by hiding out, she may have [? told ?] it, by hiding out in the house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So she escaped to the address that I had also, that I myself had prepared beforehand possibly for my parents should the need arise.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now we started corresponding with each other by using the business envelopes of my-- our benefactor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And her-- the gentleman where she-- at the house where she was hiding out, he used his envelopes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that was the way how we could correspond with each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In the evening we listened to the British radio.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And it became quite clear to us-- to all three of us-- that this would be a long, long war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Very long.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And increasingly, Max and I were talking about our hiding out there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We noticed the goings-on in the evening, when we were allowed to come down to the private quarters of our friend, that underground figures came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "A newspaper, underground newspaper which still exists today, was founded in that house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And all kind of measures were deliberated about in his apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Money was collected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Max and I became aware of the grave danger that we were in-- but especially so our benefactor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if at any time someone, let's say, surprised us by-- by coming up unannounced, which fortunately never happened, they would see two-- two men hiding out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The life of our-- our friend wouldn't be worth a cent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would be lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so were we.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we started thinking of escaping.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
